{"tid":1703003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"三罷前夕 可以做嘅嘢","createTime":"2019-11-10T05:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T05:07:47.000Z","uid":336091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d83e569483947ffe8cad72a395ddd48be3afa91","tid":1703003,"uid":336091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"想同一啲唔敢罷 唔敢升級嘅人講你地可以做啲咩<br />\n拿我唔係要屌你地，但你地其實就算返工都有嘢可以做到<br />\n麻煩聽日唔敢罷工嘅人全部同我帶住一至兩個gip去搭車，試諗下如果半架車嘅人都拎住個gip入車廂，好肯定會有一大班唔理三罷嘅港豬/藍屍上唔到車<br />\n唔洗你地做塞鐵師比人屌，帶個空gip搭鐵都可以掛<br />\n<br />\n你拖一個空gip&gt;個車廂少左一個企位&gt;多一個人要等下班車&gt;下一班車又會因為多左一個人少左一個企位<br />\n你帶一個gip搭車就可以推遲到好多港豬藍屍返工嘅時間，仲可以令班車嘅載客量增加。<br />\n無本生利嘅嘢唔係唔做呀？又和平又理性又非暴力又無犯法。<br />\n<br />\n求下唔敢升級嘅和理非咁做，帶多個gip就可以令手足少啲機會受傷被捕<br />\n求下你地，如果覺得我講嘅有用麻煩跟住做同埋spread開呢個po，唔止係連登幫推，要推埋比其他年齡層知，fb/ig/wtsapp/airdrop之類"},{"pid":"273fb7cc8dcaef032e1251c444c86307b6678e79","tid":1703003,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"要一齊令1111行動成功 你而家有四樣野可以做！<br />\n<br />\n第一 推呢個post上返熱門 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696996\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696996</a><br />\n第二 幫手宣傳出去 ig/fb /WhatsApp/tg<br />\n第三 今晚幫手貼連儂牆<br />\n第四 加入返tg group <a href=\"http://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielamgroup&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=0e1d9e0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup</a><br />\n<br />\n最後聽日7:00要見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XknsjfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXknsjfF.jpg&h=083b2897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5HPxAG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5HPxAG.jpg&h=81b4f697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7TGoHn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th